Pan Kim Byung Gi vás vydíral, že?

98
00:07:07,559 --> 00:07:08,628
To říkal kdo?

99
00:07:08,628 --> 00:07:10,469
Pan Oh Tae Suk.

100
00:07:15,809 --> 00:07:19,138
