206
00:14:43,719 --> 00:14:45,719
Tak jo. Let's go!

207
00:14:47,418 --> 00:14:48,558
Tak se mi to líbí.

208
00:14:49,528 --> 00:14:50,589
To je ono.

209
00:14:54,668 --> 00:14:55,798
Supr. Hej, zpomalujete, tancujte!

210
00:14:55,798 --> 00:14:57,699
Supr. Hej, zpomalujete, tancujte!

